{"tid":1241230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【換新身份證被撤選民身份？】 【選舉事務處：入境處電腦出事遲交資料】","createTime":"2019-06-18T15:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T16:28:03.000Z","uid":34522,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c9d64551b707b633bfe6efaccaa65eb7ad16da5","tid":1241230,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"【換新身份證被撤選民身份？】<br />\n【選舉事務處：入境處電腦出事遲交資料】<br />\n<br />\n市民正分批換領新的智能身份證，但有已換證的選民就發現，自己不在選民登記冊內。<br />\n選舉事務處解釋，是入境處電腦系統出問題，遲了轉交資料。<br />\n但據了解，入境處認為，有否傳送更新資料，與選民身份無關。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #選舉事務處 #入境處 #智能身份證 #選民 #登記 #翻查<br />\n<br />\n今次到左選舉事務處同入境處傳波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2393483b3944e78748b00a3e3503755e66082235","tid":1241230,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cd15806a7caa48b9cdee38b95945a91edfd166","tid":1241230,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"個個部門都傳一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90fdfe7313e88f409bc09d7ae0ee9a705ce3a1d","tid":1241230,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:53:40.000Z","msg":"可以推落郵政署話寄唔出通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2d0131a62d08e914dd51746fc9ffb64adfb47d","tid":1241230,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:28:03.000Z","msg":"連呢啲都學人玩割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}